  "url": "https://www.ada.lk/breaking_news/\u0db8\u0dc4\u0dcf-\u0dc3\u0d82\u0d9d\u0dbb\u0dad\u0dca\u0db1\u0dba-\u0daf\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dca-\u0d85\u0dc0\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0daf-\u0db4\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0d9a\u0dba\u0db1\u0dca-\u0db4\u0dd2\u0dc5\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dd0\u0daf\u0dca\u0daf\u0dda-\u0db1\u0dd1/11-394957",
  "time_ut": 1656503486,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0db8\u0dc4\u0dcf \u0dc3\u0d82\u0d9d\u0dbb\u0dad\u0dca\u0db1\u0dba \u0daf\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dca \u0d85\u0dc0\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0daf \u0db4\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0d9a\u0dba\u0db1\u0dca \u0db4\u0dd2\u0dc5\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dd0\u0daf\u0dca\u0daf\u0dda \u0db1\u0dd1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The rulers did not heed the advice given by the Maha Sangha",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Ven. Warakagoda Gnanaratana Thero, the Chief Incumbent of the Asgiriya Chapter said that the current situation in the country is due to the disobedience of the admonition given by the Maha Sangha to the rulers of Sri Lanka.",
        "He was speaking at a function held at a temple in Madawala, Kandy.",
        "The Supreme Buddha was also insulted. The monks are a group of people who can endure humiliation and work. There are many people living with sinful ideas who resent noble services .Many people say that only a few people can think intelligently and understand that this is good and this is bad .Therefore most people can be considered as extremists.",
        "Even the little children here today know the tragedy that has befallen our country today and know the reason for it. We have nothing to do but worry about it. But we seemed to ignore them. If it goes this way, this country will be on the verge of destruction. We explained all that to them. But it is very clear that they are not caring about them. Therefore, the monks of the country have realized that it is useless to go and talk about something that is not done. All educated people are worried about the situation in this country.",
        "When those parents think about the future of their children, they all grieve as parents. Sorry. But there is nothing that can be done. There is no human being who can worship the Buddha and respect the three gems, except to say to God .People do not care. Therefore, all we have to do is worship the Buddha, give thanks to God and tell God to protect this country. The Supreme Buddha must have known this. God Sakra entrusted the task to Lord Vishnu. Therefore, the protection of this country is entrusted to the deities including the god Sakara and the god Vishnu.",
        "If we do good deeds as Buddhists, we will get the protection of those gods and goddesses. Energy alone plays the role of protecting our country. Looking at the disasters that have befallen the country in the recent past, one can be satisfied with the extent to which this country is.",
        "Given this situation, we can never be happy about our future. It's useless to worry about that. Victory or defeat must be endured. Buddhism teaches about death and impermanence. That understanding has been given to all of us through Dhamma schools."
      ],
